  <num>7-705.03</num>
  <heading>Court costs and attorney’s fees.</heading>
  <text>The court shall award costs and reasonable attorney’s fees to a resident who prevails in an action brought under § <cite path="§7-705.01">7-705.01</cite> or § <cite path="§7-705.02">7-705.02</cite>.</text>
